{"type": "article", "id": 56134, "title": "Farfetch 计划 IPO 融资 6 亿美元，以及，Pantone 发布 2019 春季色彩趋势 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-09-06T07:58:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29870, "name": "Garage Magazine"}, {"id": 52560, "name": "W Magazine"}, {"id": 3351, "name": "Miu Miu"}, {"id": 977, "name": "Tom Ford"}, {"id": 52561, "name": "布拉格时装周"}, {"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 574557, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180906145544FQhtvP58BCrWG2TE.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.nasdaq.com/article/luxury-online-fashion-site-farfetch-sets-terms-for-600-million-us-ipo-cm1018310\" rel=\"nofollow\">英国奢侈品电商 Farfetch 公布 IPO 计划，预计融资 6 亿美元</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Farfetch 向美国 SEC 递交的招股显示，该集团将在美国发行 3750 万股 A 类普通股，每股定价在 15 - 17 美元之间。截止 6 月 30 日，Farfetch 过去 12 个月销售额达 4.81 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://news.winshang.com/html/064/5716.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Ralph Lauren 在中国市场推出品牌官方线上旗舰店</strong></a>&nbsp;| 旗舰店于 9 月 5 日正式上线，涵盖 男士 Purple Label 系列与女士 Collection 系列产品，此外还将与微信公众号进行整合，以优化线上服务。<br></p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-burberry-strategy/burberry-to-stop-burning-unsold-goods-removes-real-fur-from-collections-idUSKCN1LM0MU\" rel=\"nofollow\">Burberry 表示将不再焚烧积压库存，并将停止使用动物皮草</a>&nbsp;</strong>| Burberry CEO&nbsp;Marco Gobbetti 对路透社表示，“当代奢侈（modern luxury）意味着承担社会和环境责任，这是 Burberry 的核心信念，对于品牌的长远成功而言至关重要。”他还表示，将追随 Versace、Gucci、Stella McCartney 的步伐，不再使用兔毛、狐狸毛、貂皮和浣熊皮等动物皮草。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><strong><a href=\"http://us.fashionnetwork.com/news/Jo-Malone-unveils-first-namesake-scent-for-Jo-Loves-to-celebrate-25-years-in-fragrance,1010532.html#.W5DRUZMzZp8\" rel=\"nofollow\">为庆祝从业 25 周年，Jo Malone 创始人首次推出同名香水&nbsp;Jo by Jo Loves</a></strong>。<br></p><p>这也是 Jo Malone 首次像&nbsp;Pat McGrath 和 Kylie Jenner 等人那样，将自己置于产品营销的核心。根据官方介绍，Jo by Jo Loves 结合了 Malone 本人最爱的两样东西：经典红和西柚。前调为苦橙、青柠和留兰香，中调为希蒂莺（<em>Hedione）</em>和黑椒，后调为愈创木、雪松和香根草。零售价为 105 美元/ 50 ml，170 美元/ 100 ml。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061513584dbORJ6ghGIAMutk.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"0.907692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/news/garage-magazine-rihanna-cover-publication-050918\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rihanna 登上 Garage Magazine 最新一期封面。</a></strong></p><p>摄影师：Deana Lawson；造型师：Carlos Nazario；Rihanna 身着古着玫瑰上衣、Tiffany 项链、D&amp;G 短裤及 Y/Project&nbsp;高跟鞋。Deana Lawson 善于在高级成衣与廉价布景的搭配中寻找平衡，利用光影和色彩突出人物气质。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906132025BW5rVxhUAGuokdZ2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.wmagazine.com/gallery/cate-blanchett-female-photographers-artists-cover-story\" rel=\"nofollow\">W Magazine 2018 年第五期邀请 Cate Blanchett 担任客座主编</a></strong>。</p><p>该期也是 W Magazine 创刊以来首次由全女性团队制作，拍摄对象也均为女性。这个主意由杂志总监&nbsp;Stefano Tonchi 最先提出，他认为女性权利和女性主义话题会有不错的市场表现。不过他也<a href=\"https://wwd.com/business-news/media/cate-blanchett-all-female-issue-w-magazine-1202783686/\" rel=\"nofollow\">对《女装日报》解释说</a>：“这不是什么政治表态——Cate 对此毫无兴趣。这更像是在导演一出所有角色均由女性扮演的戏剧，与爱德华时代所有女性角色均由男性扮演的做法相对。”</p><p>选择 Cate Blanchett 的另一个原因是这位女演员向来不受主流时尚媒体青睐，人们认为她“太老，对于时尚杂志封面而言形象过于经典”。Stefano Tonchi 则相信，她能够更深入地与团队合作。事实也的确如此：9 位女性艺术家及摄影师与这位客座主编共同创造了一系列别具风格的影像。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135141LzMlAgBVyo6rsmn3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.300296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135158Kb6u8FwEQosxgLGa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.300296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061352086EpyBto2RXHaWiP4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.477811\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135219E3Ry5fj07QGmO6wN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.300296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135236h2fy3xg1EtpmdaKQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.300296\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018090613525408m1LXcZ7adCfI5b.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135301xndkDr3XR8u04ab7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135309wyi8akXEK6SfLQZc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135316Y2fCOpHaZWsyl5Bg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135322oRvIL3s180QK6Djz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018090613533590TkAq6QY5PpWixh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135413Y9ryqBDAjMvs6XeU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135512Ebcp5xZJlS7X8MqH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135523Iwnt7SvhRPapxD4X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.649408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906135535F6RuZ3E7xkJdIPTt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.683432\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/fashion-news/shows-reviews/gallery/tom-ford-rtw-spring-1202786446/\" rel=\"nofollow\">纽约时装周开幕，首场发布&nbsp;Tom Ford 2019 春夏成衣系列。</a></strong><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061406438D9y74qFKXfBntx2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061406549OzgH80JiEteX1YF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140659N6gUVaBQuOGdJcwl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140705hsVoaF85PYwcplW9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061407114SiUPrwbxHqLK2cQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140716zDJWpO45dLXB1EZ9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140722u7xXiy38GV6dISgP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140728RZqtTENyg1C69M5P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140736nOpUq3K6yzaDXSMj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140745dGZzNpIQMVjo19tk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140753OL1jAow2fDaSKEYq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140759yHAwrVvgIfxk1Ded.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061408097VjvkqXhzrDFEtGa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140815XFfTC6qHaJi04LrI.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140822G2PfWzsNAypjrgce.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140832hEyguNARsJqK562m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140841opjdbZx9RD3m5CWG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140847jNbsX7gpUz8OxrAh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906140857DJEFQYLNXvVbchHk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/eye/lifestyle/empowering-colors-top-pantone-spring-color-trend-report-for-nyfw-1202783221/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pantone 发布纽约时装周 2019 春季色彩趋势报告。</a></strong></p><p>报告称，本季最流行的五种颜色均以红调或橘调为主，包括&nbsp;Fiesta, Jester Red, Turmeric, Living Coral 和 Pink Peacock。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906153629mDuaFbChIqHnY5cA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.083008\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Fiesta</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061536406rDEog8R7Jeqma0l.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.083008\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Jester Red</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906153650tu28p7qBH4NKPXGR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.083008\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Turmeric</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906153703JF654xhTEUj2VA8o.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.083008\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>Living Coral&nbsp;</figcaption> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906153713yH1LxZgWOY5w3zDB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.083008\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><figcaption>&nbsp;Pink Peacock</figcaption> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"http://www.anothermag.com/fashion-beauty/11100/up-closer-and-personal-with-the-girls-of-miu-miu-aw18\" rel=\"nofollow\">Miu Miu 发布 2018 年秋冬系列广告片</a>。</strong><br></p><p>影片主题为<strong>“</strong>Other Conversations”，在 SONY Portapak 手提式录影摄影机上录制。模特们都梳着美国 60 年代摇滚女歌手&nbsp;Ronnie Spector 式的经典蜂窝头，旁白则用一种慵懒的美国口音穿过信号不佳的电话线赞美不同发型的好处。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=x07780mjdn4\"></iframe> </figure> </div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906141227fHzkF8oBuJhp1LPq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.303906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906141241ny4wqJAk3oL06BUC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.303333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906141247U05XzW7oLlu9qyGa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.303906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061412559Lk2PUS70z5cJKID.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.303906\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906141322y2IkQxg3NYCoqG1P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.652344\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906141330NmSTYMGFBZQ0yzrs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.652344\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906141335c0poEifwI3xr4emH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.652344\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906141342otYJ193mAaOkInNw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.652344\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906141350BKhlUegc06CWIaqt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.652344\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/2018/9/prague-fashion-week-spring-summer-2019-street-style\" rel=\"nofollow\">布拉格 2019 春夏时装周正在克拉姆·葛拉斯宫（Clam-Gallas Palace）举行</a></strong>，潮流媒体 Hypebeast 推出了时装周期间的街拍合集。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143142DxYgEcPaN23SMKTL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143103gStyqbv7rocIW0Ud.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143117d4kxTFDSYumW9KnZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143153cz61TsPKJ4CQFuDm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143216xXLcNQzCSFvTGuig.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143224mGcX960wWE4OekSq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143232DQyUpJ9oVi7TesYB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143241Wi2Vt1ACmRHTBlqe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143252BqNZiCbu6lPsAFtW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143259h5sRpMo4U83Dtr9y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809061433060gwPR9LOvmzqNeSa.png\" data-ratio=\"0.570647\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143431pVl8yULXnmufROAk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143439vylthiSVqkdD9gAn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>一个专门记录戴妃离婚后穿搭的 Instagram 账号<strong>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ladydirevengelooks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">@ladydirevengelooks</a></strong>。</p><p>账号运营者 Eloise Moran <a href=\"http://www.anothermag.com/fashion-beauty/11096/the-instagram-account-chronicling-princess-dianas-post-divorce-looks\" rel=\"nofollow\">在接受 Another Magazine 采访时说</a>：“分手、离开那些让你自轻自贱的人以后，女孩们往往打扮得比以前好看 20 倍。这就像是复仇一样……我觉得很多戴安娜没能公开说出来的话，都通过她的衣着说出来了。”<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143559xnKejNasdGhAWHoO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.245552\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143614AOKfuIMixHVa7S34.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.136000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180906143631CJmz0LTD596lAO8V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.249333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>题图来自<a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/news/garage-magazine-rihanna-cover-publication-050918\" rel=\"nofollow\"> itsnicethat.com</a></p>"}